data.title: Fs Airports
data.meta_description: Fs Airports - Free ebook download as Text File (.txt), PDF File (.pdf) or read book online for free. The document contains location codes for airports and airfields in Afghanistan, Albania, Algeria, American Samoa, Angola, Anguilla, Antarctica, Antigua and Barbuda, and Argentina. Each entry lists the country, location name, IATA code, and ICAO code. There are over 200 entries in total covering multiple countries.
